iv>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"sgxmgx\">\n<a href=\"/user/sgxmgx\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/15/25/152526.jpg?r=1708518084&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/sgxmgx\" class=\"l\">セパラ</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars6\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 搁置 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2024-12-18 10:13</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">可以看出手游的制作很有心，比如loading界面的CG动画，英雄界面的3D建模特写，以及2D立绘的动态效果，游戏内的镜像地图、科技龙、技能重做。但是发行时间还是太晚了，如今手游圈里MOBA并不是主流，首选的MOBA手游也不是它（话虽如此，但背靠腾讯，也不会掉出前50）。</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_35140020\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"627854\">\n<a href=\"/user/627854\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/62/78/627854_Lhzjw.jpg?r=1766919761&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/627854\" class=\"l\">青木琉璃_21</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars2\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2024-11-23 14:57</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">pc游是好的 手游是神必的 机制是恶心的 拿着端游的底子装着农药的机制 给人整出恶心是最懂的 QQ区的更是灾难 的 游戏的本质是什么算是给你该明白了 （黄豆流汗）一天体验完游戏 消耗完期待值 两星是给这破手游的底子 pc游起码八星以上</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_34914223\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<template id=\"likes_reaction_grid_item\" type=\"text/template\">\n    <a class=\"item {selected_class}\"\n          href=\"javascript:void(0);\"\n          data-like-type=\"{type}\"\n          data-like-main-id=\"{main_id}\"\n          data-like-related-